==Description==
Fourth and final resident of the [[Rabbibunny Village]] in the [[Hamalayi Mountains]]. 

he gives Twinsen a clue of the location of the [[Clear Water Lake]] by saying it is 'very near here.'

Found standing at the edge of the village, by a car track that leads to the [[Mutant Factory]].
Very unimportant character, however before [[Twinsen]] destroys the Mutant Factory, each time he encounter this villager he is being attacked by a mutant, and whenever Twinsen saves him from the mutant he is rewarded with a clover.

After Twinsen destroys the Mutant Factory this villager can be seen walking up and down the carrot garden in the village.

